intent.user_query: Which customer has the highest average purchase quantity?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName, AVG(sd.Quantity) AS AveragePurchaseQuantity FROM fitness_db.Customers c JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON c.CustomerID = s.CustomerID JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON s.SaleID = sd.SaleID GROUP BY c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName ORDER BY AveragePurchaseQuantity DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY AveragePurchaseQuantity DESC) <= 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName, AVG(sd.Quantity) AS AveragePurchaseQuantity FROM fitness_db.Customers c JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON c.CustomerID = s.CustomerID JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON s.SaleID = sd.SaleID GROUP BY c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName ORDER BY AveragePurchaseQuantity DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY AveragePurchaseQuantity DESC) <= 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
